Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.72,0:00:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Fiore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A neutral country of 17 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a world of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is bought and sold there every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an integral part of people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are those who use magic as their occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are referred to as wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:34.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wizards belong to various guilds \Nand perform jobs on commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:38.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a large number of guilds within the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a certain city there lies a certain guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:49.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild from which various legends were once born... Or \Nrather, will continue to be born long into the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And its name is:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:55.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:06.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:16.13,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Can you hear this voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:21.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! It's hoarse from yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:25.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Until your heart can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:29.48,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:34.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon and sun high-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:39.18,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:44.58,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're not here to make me laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.72,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,even what I'm looking for can't be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:51.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowing, be honest with yourself and smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:56.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,because when two people lay close, time overlaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:07.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:27.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail! {note: I've been using "last time"... but it's clearly meant more generically so I'll switch it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Save my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Macao back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:37.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Gray... lend me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:39.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tag along, but I have one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get back, let's have a match!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:46.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:54.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisenwald may have been destroyed, but the root of the problem still remains unresolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:58.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of dark guilds rivals that of the stars themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:01.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should come up with a plan to wipe them all out at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:02.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not stand for Zeref's magic falling into their hands again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:13.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And how was it that they obtained such magic so easily in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:17.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blame goes all the way up to the administrative level. {They're bureaucrats playing the blame game here}{note: perhaps "regulators"?  I believe this is refering to some body that is in charge of monitoring powerful magical items like lullaby...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:18.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:24.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like this time we were saved by that thorn in our sides, Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:29.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They destroyed a whole dark guild with just 4 or 5 people. Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:35.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's not something you want to accept, but that's reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We would be in dire straits if the Lullaby had actually killed those guild masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:45.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have cost the heads of many of us standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:49.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! You intend to lay blame even on the Council itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:55.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their tendency for wanton destruction gives me headaches! This time too! {The literal is "makes me want to cover my head" in fear or confusion}{check/edit... something isn't right about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:04:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... We must repay them for their kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu vs. Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident with Eisenwald targeting the guild masters during their regular meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:20.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,became big news immediately and everyone in the country learned of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:25.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have never believed I'd be at the center of such a huge event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:29.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I'm living my day to day life just like I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:33.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I think back on what happened and get all excited, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:40.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got wind that most of Eisenwald's members were arrested, including that guy named Kage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:46.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The one thing that scares me is they don't seem to have caught Erigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:50.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do if he comes to take revenge on Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:56.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be okay! Natsu, Erza, and Gray are Fairy Tail's strongest team!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus: Happy and I are there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:03.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guild's the best, so don't worry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this a secret from Dad, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:15.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll do some shopping today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:20.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thrilling adventures are great and all, but you can't beat relaxing at home! {I think I understand why you put it in there, but "and exciting" adds nothing to the sentence}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:24.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rent for this place is 70,000 jewel? That's really cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You found yourself a nice pad, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trespassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't strip in other people's homes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! It's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was already naked when I arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:42.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd forget, so I came to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:42.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, you forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:48.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu said so before we left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight, Erza! {It's hard to hear these and they aren't in the script...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:52.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and Erza are fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, they were serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Hi, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Serious as can be! If they didn't take this seriously, they couldn't call themselves men!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's a woman, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More like a female monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if two of the people in the strongest team clash...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:13.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Strongest team?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Natsu, and Erza, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the top three in Fairy Tail, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's just dumb. Who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was Mira-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:28.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You made her cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do recognize Natsu's and Gray's manly spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:35.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wouldn't go calling them the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:39.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a ton more strong people in Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like me, for example!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:44.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza {\i1}is{\i0} probably the strongest woman, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:48.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're talking about the strongest man, it's probably Mystogan or Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:53.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that Natsu, Gray, and Erza worked the best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:59.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Weren't you saying how you were always worried Gray and Natsu would fight without Erza around?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, I think this will be an interesting battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I expect Erza to win easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:10.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been since we've pitted our magic head to head like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a kid then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things will be different this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day! I'm going to beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't plan on holding back. {Where'd the "Don't worry" come from?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I truly tested my own limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Empress Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That armor resists fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:45.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's flames effectiveness are halved! {I don't recognize her from the manga} {wait, does this small character always talk like the world is an RPG game?  If that's the case then use "That armor reduces Natsu's flame damage by 50%!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, that's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll betting on Erza after all. That okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a heartless cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:58.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this sort of thing! I don't want either one to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:07:59.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're unexpectedly innocent, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:02.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Empress Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:06.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, guess I have go full power, no holding back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you it would be a good battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:31.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "good" about it? {sarcasm takes time to parse in text, so here is not the best place.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:43.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:49.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a messenger from the Council. {I used "envoy" but messenger works just as well}{alt: "Emissary"... but usually that is only used for representative of heads of state in english emissary of the king/president, etc... the Council is still apart from the government itself, so...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Council?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:51.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A messenger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they send one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:56.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're ignoring the scene in front of them, aren't they?  {check me?  This usage of "visual" I've never encountered... can't find in dictionary}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:09:03.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stemming from the recent Eisenwald incident, we hereby charge you with 11 counts of criminal property damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza Scarlet, you are under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say {\i1}what{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out! Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:34.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just go on a rampage if we let you out. {In this world, people can actually blow up. How about "go on a rampage"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:39.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't! So turn me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, you'll go to rescue her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:44.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't! Who cares about Erza anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:48.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Council we're dealing with here. This one's out of our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out! I have something I want to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:55.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Council or no Council, those guys were the bad ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:59.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're innocent and the Council says you're guilty, then you're guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously think they'd listen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:06.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've done all that stuff before... Why this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:12.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be... Got to be something behind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:19.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Council's Fiore Branch. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:23.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where judgment will be passed on Erza, but just then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Siegrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a thought projection. {You could say "astral bodies" I suppose, but I think Thought Projection is better. Everybody who is very high level can do it, but Siegrain is better than most at it}{is there a standard way for translating "shinen tai" that you use?  Maybe related to seigrain's magic ability?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:49.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is now in ERA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:54.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The old men in the next room are also all thought projections.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:57.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they'd actually come all the way here for such a trivial matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:58.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all your doing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pointless farce!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:07.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be harsh. After all, I'm on Fairy Tail's side. {"Preposterous" doesn't quite work after "Pointles farce." And I don't think he meant it as being FT's lawyer.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The old men were afraid that they would share in the blame,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so they created a plan to push responsibility onto others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Scapegoating," if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish. {"Whatever" has recently taken on the "voice" of a whiney teenager.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:24.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see you before the trial and warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say nothing of the past to the old men. {Their link is in the past. This wording is still vague enough to raise questions}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For both our sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:38.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting on the other side of the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:46.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know some powerful people, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:56.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:00.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not after I've come this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:14.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now commence this Wizard's Trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:20.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The accused, Erza Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:24.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:32.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stay here! Let's go testify on her behalf!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:33.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:35.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This arrest is an injustice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:40.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they decide on a verdict, it'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:44.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how fast we go, if we leave now we won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:45.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out! I said, let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:51.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you want out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:59.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Natsu? You suddenly run out of steam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I owed Natsu one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:16.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to pose as Natsu, I transformed myself into a gecko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:20.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad caught Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:23.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to it! I'll pretend to be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, where's the real Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:27.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't go after Erza, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:33.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy might actually try and punch a council member!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:38.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will wait patiently for the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:44.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The accused, Erza Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:48.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In regards to the recent incident involving Eisenwald and the Lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:52.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will answer to charges concerning the damage to parts of Oshibana Station,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:55.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the destruction of the Ryusika Gorge railway,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the complete collapse of the Clover Meeting Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:01.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are accused of these acts of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to witnesses at the scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the culprit was an armored female wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:16.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the armored female wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:19.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to catch me, then just try!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Erza!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I did somethin' wrong, then spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:32.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the crime had better be worse than murdering the guild masters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them to the jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, don't apologize to these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:49.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, wait... I AM ERZA!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:56.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:59.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a formality!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A formality?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:02.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They arrested me just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:05.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to preserve the order of the magical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:09.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The council must make a show of enforcing law among wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:12.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:15.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that they'll find me guilty, but there won't be any real punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd probably have been back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:19.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't gone nuts, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:27.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:32.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! {How about: "Your armor hurts!" or "Your hugs hurt!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:37.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So he was in Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu Dragneel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the sweet smell of freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just smell it, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:50.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew freedom was so great?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:51.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:51.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:54.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what makes him so lovable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:58.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was all an arrest for show...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:03.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! She's a scapegoat but not a sacrificial lamb! {It reads like a typo. How about: "She's a scapegoat but not a sacrifical lamb!"} {pretty close, I think.  Meaning is the same at least}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an ice wizard, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That joke gave me the chills...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:11.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about your man-to-man battle with Erza, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, let's continue where we left off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's strong, that's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,..m... sl..p....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...s him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:57.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:19.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to undo the sleeping magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:26.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:28.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:32.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:40.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels like... Was Mystogan here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:41.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:44.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He always uses such super powerful magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:45.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:49.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the strongest men in Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:54.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He does this because he doesn't like other people to see his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:58.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When he comes to take a job, he always puts everyone to sleep like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that? That's way too suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So no one other than the master knows what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I know what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:11.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:12.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one of the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:19.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan's shy. Keep your noses outta it! {There was a missing line here, so you will want to extend the off time}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:24.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus! Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just beat by Erza a second ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:31.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! If you can't even beat Erza, there's no way you could beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you implying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:35.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, calm down there, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That I am the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:40.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then get down here and prove it, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:51.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot go upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:54.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you've made him angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus, enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:19:01.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up my seat as the strongest in Fairy Tail for anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to Erza or Mystogan, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:06.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About what Master said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:15.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How he can't go up to the second floor. Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit early to talk to you about it, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the second-floor request board has jobs posted to it so difficult they don't even compare to the ones on the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S class quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S class?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are jobs where the slightest mistake would mean death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the rewards are correspondingly high.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:40.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only wizards who the master approves can take on S class quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:46.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you include Erza, Laxus, and Mystogan, then there are only 5 people who can do them. {5 including those three, Gildarts and potentially Mirajane}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:50.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S class is not really something you should seek out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:54.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all jobs where you'd need a great number of lives! {a cat's nine lives isn't gamey. I think what made that gamey is using both words together, "infinite lives"}{edit me... this seems to video gamey... lit is even worse?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:56.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:59.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your step, missy! {This is a running joke that will come up again and again}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:03.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of both Mystosan and Laxus before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail really is an amazing guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:10.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think I know how everyone ranks in power about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna work hard starting tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell like a gym!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna weight lift, do it in your own house!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:25.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? We're a team, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:26.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:28.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You like pink, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:30.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but I don't care about barbells!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:34.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to get more powerful if we're gonna beat Erza and Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:38.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter to me, now leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna train all night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:45.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:49.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do an S class quest, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:51.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S class!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:53.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:55.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you couldn't go up to the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:58.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We went up and took one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:04.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's our first time, so we picked the cheapest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it's still 7 million jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:10.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! We don't have permission to do an S class.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:14.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do this right, then gramps'll have to recognize us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you're always doing crazy things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At least follow the rules of your own guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:25.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, I'll never get to go up to the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:28.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I can't go. You two enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a job where we're supposed to rescue an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:31.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An island?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:38.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Galuna, the cursed island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm definitely not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:42.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I offer to give you half the fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:43.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not an incentive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch. We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:47.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:49.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go cool your heads a little, sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Leave using the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:55.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They left the poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:58.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, now it looks like {\i1}I{\i0} stole it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:00.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:05.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, way! You also get one of the 12 Gold Gate keys? {I know they mean the Zodiac constellations, but I don't think they ever called it that}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:13.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Happy, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:16.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:21.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the requests on the second floor disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:28.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me away to someplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:33.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride on a tin horse, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:36.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.47,0:22:44.06,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad that my beloved doll can't talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:46.43,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:51.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I think of you tears start to flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:56.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a crybaby, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:59.46,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,In the moon (the moon) at night (at night)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:01.20,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always (I'm always)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:04.50,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,searching for the rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:07.18,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:09.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,so much it's like I'm under a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:12.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This love is a monologue
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:15.11,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,from which I'll never awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:17.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:20.34,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,since I've completely fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:23.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what spell I could chant,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:25.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to get through to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.56,0:23:29.51,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Spouting this and that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:36.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just love you like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:39.28,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,One day I want to be able to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:41.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"You got me."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:45.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,My words of thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:54.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, which should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:24:00.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:03.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our first time, so let's do the simplest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.01,0:24:03.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:06.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this Galuna Island one?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.15,0:24:09.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that Lucy would want this extra reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.54,0:24:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.99,0:24:12.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's decide on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.48,0:24:13.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.68,0:24:16.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Cursed Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:21.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go lift weights at Lucy's house until we go on the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.03,0:24:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like a work out to get you invigorated!
